snippet.title: "A View From The Cloud" at the UN Church Center, 5-17-17 - Conversation 2: Finance
snippet.description:
Amber Nystrom, Co-Founder, Partner, Prosparity; 3:00 Paula di Perna, global environmental policy advisor; 7:42 Vinicius Pinheiro, International Labour Organisation UN Representative. 
12:21 Innovators introduced by Amber Nystrom: 14:30 Mackenzie Colgan, Regional Director, ImpactAssets; 16:28 Torian Richardson, Board President, MineED; 18:02 Holly Ruxin, CEO, Montcalm TCR.
Moderator, Shamina de Gonzaga, Executive Director, World Council of Peoples for the United Nations. More information at StreamingMuseum.org and WCPUN.org
